com.usamd.modelBean

Class AbstractBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.usamd.modelBean.AbstractBean
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractUserBean, AddressBean, BMICategoryBean, HealthCenterBean, MedicineInfoBean, SectionUIBean

    public abstract class AbstractBean
extends java.lang.Object
    This class acts as a model bean for carrying common information like create user and update user details. This bean also holds bean constants.
    Author:
    USAWebMD
